    {
      "id": "2042440656526983235",
      "text": "How can you empathize with founders if you don't build stuff yourself?\n\nThis was one advantage of running HN while I was running YC. It was an enormous schlep, but it meant I was dealing daily with the same problems as the founders.",
      "created_at": "Fri Apr 10 03:12:53 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2042440656526983235",
      "likes": 479,
      "retweets": 26,
      "replies": 41,
      "quotes": 3,
      "bookmarks": 95,
      "views": 71344,
      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": true,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2042438925957153231",
      "text": "200th dive. Now I'm in the danger zone, where I feel like I know what I'm doing, but actually don't.",
      "created_at": "Fri Apr 10 03:06:01 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2042438925957153231",
      "likes": 279,
      "retweets": 2,
      "replies": 28,
      "quotes": 0,
      "bookmarks": 18,
      "views": 48084,
      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": false,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2042438230994542677",
      "text": "Later stage investors always grumble about increasing valuations. But there is some basis in reality for it: companies do grow faster now.",
      "created_at": "Fri Apr 10 03:03:15 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2042438230994542677",
      "likes": 184,
      "retweets": 6,
      "replies": 11,
      "quotes": 3,
      "bookmarks": 26,
      "views": 50437,
      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": true,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2041812497410543910",
      "text": "No one in our family can tell lemons from limes with their eyes closed. We all thought we could, but no one could.\n\nI bet all bartenders know this.",
      "created_at": "Wed Apr 08 09:36:49 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2041812497410543910",
      "likes": 2363,
      "retweets": 21,
      "replies": 269,
      "quotes": 46,
      "bookmarks": 243,
