      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": false,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2041363640499200353",
      "text": "Since there's yet another article claiming that we \"removed\" Sam because partners distrusted him, no, we didn't. It's not because I want to defend Sam that I keep insisting on this. It's because it's so annoying to read false accounts of my own actions.",
      "created_at": "Tue Apr 07 03:53:13 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2041363640499200353",
      "likes": 2491,
      "retweets": 93,
      "replies": 69,
      "quotes": 15,
      "bookmarks": 398,
      "views": 338844,
      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": true,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2041366050693173393",
      "text": "I'm also tired of people misrepresenting that quote about parachuting him into an island full of cannibals. I didn't mean anything sinister by it, just that he's an example of someone with \"toughness, adaptability, and determination\". See for yourself:\n\nhttps://t.co/Nnqdwrkffr",
      "created_at": "Tue Apr 07 04:02:47 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2041366050693173393",
      "likes": 366,
      "retweets": 9,
