    },
    {
      "id": "2038923415218962785",
      "text": "This interview with Jessica goes the deepest of any interview she's done into her life story, and how it gave her the unique combination of qualities that made Y Combinator work.",
      "created_at": "Tue Mar 31 10:16:38 +0000 2026",
