      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2038901705543426524",
      "text": "Sadly, he doesn't even have this advantage, as anyone who's had small children knows. When someone is sufficiently unsophisticated, it's possible to know what they're doing even when they don't know themselves. https://t.co/H1QLbIR8BI",
      "created_at": "Tue Mar 31 08:50:22 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2038901705543426524",
      "likes": 2501,
      "retweets": 177,
