      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2034639964319654041",
      "text": "A rule of thumb that has served me well: Beware of anything with \"innovation\" in the name.",
      "created_at": "Thu Mar 19 14:35:43 +0000 2026",
      "url": "https://twitter.com/paulg/status/2034639964319654041",
      "likes": 2004,
      "retweets": 115,
      "replies": 218,
      "quotes": 24,
      "bookmarks": 219,
      "views": 92668,
      "is_retweet": false,
      "is_reply": false,
      "is_quote": false,
      "lang": "en",
      "hashtags": [],
      "mentions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "2034553236582027580",
      "text": "Rippling is going to be one of the main companies where AI meets organizations. They're still young enough to embrace AI thoroughly, but they're also big enough that they touch organizations in many places.",
      "created_at": "Thu Mar 19 08:51:06 +0000 2026",
